<br>
Return to Felwithe and ask someone to show you where the magician's guild is.  Try /who mag while in Greater Faydark (outside Felwithe) and ask via /tells some of the mages for advice.<br>
<br>
I assume you have scribed and memorized your starting spells.  If not, you need to do so.  If you have not tried the tutorial, I strongly recommend it, it will walk you through some of the basic mechanics of the game.<br>
<br>
You've never indicated you've begged/asked anyone for money or gear, this is GOOD.  Explaining you are new and asking simple questions will sometimes yield gifts, but it is extremely impolite to come right out and ask for items.  /cheer you for not having done this <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
