<br>
Likewise, if you click on an item the merchant has for sale, test will appear that tells you how much the merchant wants for that item.<br>
<br>
The mage guild in Felwithe is in the second city zone, not the first city zone you enter from GFay.  You go back to the left past the bait shop and through a tunnel to zone into the second Felwithe zone with the 3 guilds.  When you get there, step toward the image on the wall that is the ball between two hands.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=draccaviir>Dracca Viir</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.boomspeed.com/apothokeri/staricon.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 4<br> <font color=#333333>(1/3/03 7:18:23 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerthelibrary.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=31.topic&index=11>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.boomspeed.com/apothokeri/DraccaPhoto2.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   NO!</span><hr size=1> I have NEVER begged for anything.  Actually, since I have no room for anything, *I* am the one running up to people and giving them stuff and/or dropping bags of loot in the middle of people, LOL! <br>
