Other vendors in the mage guild will have your spells.  Move the cursor over a spell and right click it in order to get information on what level is required before you can cast the spell.  If you find a vendor with malachite (a green gemstone), buy a stack (20 pieces) of it.  You'll use up one of these each time you summon an elemental, and the first elemental spells are available at level 4.  Don't summon an elemental until you're in a zone that you intend to fight in because the elemental will die when you change zones.<br>
Finally, exit the building using the teleport pad in the mages guild.  Enter the other building in North Felwithe (the one next to the entrance tunnel) and examine the vendors there.  One of the vendors carries a number of spells that are used by the majority of spell-casting classes, and which are not found on the spell vendors in the mage's guild.<br>
